Siren's Song				KEY:Bard ~ Siren's Song						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Bard Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.LimitBreak		SOURCELINK:https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/		SORTKEY:_LimitBreakSirensSong			DESC:This Limit Break causes the bard’s music to pierce almost any barrier. For a duration of %1 rounds, any effect that would block or warp sounds such as deafened or silenced, and effects such as distort speech, is ignored for songs and bardic performance. This limit break requires only a swift action.|BardLimitBreakScaling
