Flanking Companion			KEY:Beastmaster ~ Flanking Companion			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SOURCELINK:https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/beastmaster/		TYPE:Beastmaster Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary										DESC:At 2nd level, a beastmaster chooses either Back to Back or Outflank as a bonus feat. He does not need to meet the prerequisites for this feat. He automatically grants this feat to his animal companion as well.																																																																																																																																																																							DEFINE:BeastmasterCompanionFlankingCompanion|0	BONUS:VAR|BeastmasterCompanionFlankingCompanion|1|TYPE=Boolean			BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Flanking Companion Feat|1
Empathic Link				KEY:Beastmaster ~ Empathic Link				CATEGORY:Special Ability	SOURCELINK:https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/beastmaster/		TYPE:Beastmaster Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural										DESC:At 2nd level, the beastmaster forms an empathic link with his companion out to a distance of up to 1 mile. At 6th level, the beastmaster extends his link to include not only his companion but also any animals he has befriended. The link allows the beastmaster and the animals to communicate their general emotional state (fear, hunger, happiness, curiosity) to one another. Note that the Intelligence of animals may limit what the creatures can communicate or understand.
Beastmaster Tricks			KEY:Beastmaster ~ Beastmaster Tricks			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SOURCELINK:https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/beastmaster/		TYPE:Beastmaster Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary										DESC:A beastmaster learns the use of beastmaster tricks, which typically grant a boon or bonus to the beastmaster, his animal companion, or a nearby ally. At 2nd level, the beastmaster learns one trick, selected from the list below. At 4th level, and every two levels thereafter, he learns another trick. Tricks marked an asterisk (*), only one of these talents can be used once per round.																																																																																																																																										BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Beastmaster Trick|BeastmasterLVL/2
