Teamwork Feat				KEY:Beastmaster ~ Teamwork Feat				CATEGORY:Special Ability	SOURCELINK:https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/beastmaster/		TYPE:Beastmaster Class Feature.SpecialQuality												DESC:At 3rd level and every three beastmaster levels thereafter, the beastmaster gains a bonus teamwork feat. The beastmaster must meet the prerequisites of the selected bonus teamwork feat. &nl; As a standard action, the beastmaster can choose to learn a new bonus teamwork feat in place of the most recent bonus teamwork feat he has already learned. In effect, the beastmaster loses the bonus feat in exchange for the new one. He can change only the most recent teamwork feat gained, and must meet the prerequisites for the newly selected feat. A beastmaster can change his most recent teamwork feat %1 times per day. Whenever he gains a new teamwork feat, his previous teamwork feats become permanent.|max(1,CHA)																																																																																			BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Teamwork Feat|BeastmasterLVL/3
