# Ruby Arcana
Accurate Strike			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Accurate Strike				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.173	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 2 points from his arcane pool as a swift action to resolve all of his melee weapon attacks until the end of his turn as melee touch attacks. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 9
Aquatic Agility			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Aquatic Agility				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.173	DESC:Benefit: As an immediate action, the Ruby Arcana can spend 1 point from his arcane pool to gain the benefits of water breathing for 1 round per level. During this time, he can ignore the effects of rough water and underwater combat on his attacks and movement. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 6
Arcane Accuracy			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Arcane Accuracy				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool as a swift action to grant himself an insight bonus equal to his Charisma bonus on all attack rolls until the end of his turn.
Arcane Cloak			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Arcane Cloak				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool to add his Charisma bonus to Stealth checks and Bluff checks to create a diversion in order to hide. This bonus lasts for 1 minute.
Arcane Dealer			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Arcane Dealer				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:The Ruby Arcana gains the Deadly Dealer feat, even if he does not meet the prerequisites. He can use his arcane pool to grant a deck of cards an enhancement bonus as though it were a ranged weapon with 54 pieces of ammunition. The Ruby Arcana must use either Arcane Strike or his arcane pool to enhance the cards in order to use them as weapons. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 6
Arcane Edge				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Arcane Edge					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool as an immediate action after hitting a target with a slashing or piercing weapon in order to deal an amount of bleed damage equal to his Intelligence modifier (minimum 0). Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 9
Arcane Redoubt			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Arcane Redoubt				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:As a swift action, the Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool to treat his shield bonus to AC (including any enhancement bonus) as a bonus to touch AC until the beginning of his next turn.
Arcane Redoubt, Greater		KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Arcane Redoubt (Greater)		SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:Whenever the Ruby Arcana uses his arcane redoubt ruby arcana, he may spend an additional point from his arcane pool in order to apply his shield bonus to AC (including any enhancement bonus) as a bonus on Reflex saves until the beginning of his next turn. If he is targeted with an effect requiring a Reflex save while using this power, he may spend 2 points from his arcane pool as an immediate action to grant himself evasion, or 4 points to grant himself improved evasion. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 12, arcane redoubt ruby arcana
Bane Blade				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Bane Blade					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:Whenever the Ruby Arcana enhances his weapon using his arcane pool, he may spend 1 additional point from his arcane pool to add the bane special ability to the weapon. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 15
Broad Study				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Broad Study					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:The Ruby Arcana selects another one of his spellcasting classes. The Ruby Arcana can use his spell combat abilities while casting or using spells from the spell list of that class. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 6, levels in another spellcasting class
Concentrate				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Concentrate					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can reroll any concentration check he has just made with a +4 bonus. He must use this ability after the roll is made, but before the roll's outcome is determined. The Ruby Arcana must take the second roll, even if it is worse. The Ruby Arcana can use this ability once per day.
Devoted Blade			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Devoted Blade				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:Whenever the Ruby Arcana enhances his weapon using his arcane pool, he may spend 1 additional point from his arcane pool to add either the anarchic, axiomatic, holy, or unholy special ability to the list of available options. A Ruby Arcana may only add one of these abilities if it matches his own alignment. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 12
Dispelling Strike			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Dispelling Strike				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.174	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can spend 1 or more points from his arcane pool as a swift action to imbue his weapon with a special power. If the weapon strikes a creature within the next minute, that creature is the subject of a targeted dispel using the Ruby Arcana's level as the caster level, except that this effect cannot dispel a spell of a level higher than the number of arcane pool points expended to activate this ability (treat higher-level spells as if they do not exist and apply the dispel attempt to the remaining spells with the highest caster level). Once the strike is made, the power dissipates, even if the dispel attempt is unsuccessful. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 9
Disruptive				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Disruptive					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana gains Disruptive as a bonus feat.
Enduring Blade			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Enduring Blade				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:Whenever the Ruby Arcana enchants his weapon using his arcane pool, he may spend 1 additional point from his arcane pool to increase the duration to 1 minute per Ruby Arcana level. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 6
Empowered Magic			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Empowered Magic				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Empower Spell feat. This does not increase the MP cost or the level of the spell. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 6
Familiar				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Familiar					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana gains a familiar. This familiar follows the rules for familiars presented here.
Ghost Blade				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Ghost Blade					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:Whenever the Ruby Arcana enchants his weapon using his arcane pool, he may spend 1 additional point from his arcane pool to add the brilliant energy and ghost touch special abilities to the list of available options. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 9
Hasted Assault			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Hasted Assault				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool as a swift action to move more quickly. This functions as haste, but only targets the Ruby Arcana and lasts for a number of rounds equal to the Ruby Arcana's Charisma bonus. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 9
Ki Arcana				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Ki Arcana					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana may use points from his arcana pool and ki points from a ki pool granted by another class interchangeably. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 6, must also have levels in a class that grants a ki pool
Lingering Pain			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Lingering Pain				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool as an immediate action after hitting a target with a weapon attack. All damage from that attack is considered continuous damage for the purposes of any concentration checks made by the target prior to the beginning of the Ruby Arcana's next turn.
Maneuver Mastery			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Maneuver Mastery				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana has mastered one combat maneuver. He selects one maneuver when selecting this arcana. Whenever he is attempting the selected maneuver, he uses his Ruby Arcana level in place of his base attack bonus (in addition to any base attack bonus gained from other classes). A Ruby Arcana can select this ruby arcana more than once. Its effects do not stack. Each time he selects this arcana, he selects another combat maneuver.
Maximized Magic			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Maximized Magic				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Maximize Spell feat. This does not increase the MP cost or the level of the spell. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 12
Pool Strike				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Pool Strike					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool as a standard action to charge his free hand with elemental energy. He can make a melee touch attack with that hand as a free action as part of activating this ability. If the touch attack hits, it releases the charge and deals 2d6 points of elemental damage (earth, fire, ice, lightning, water, or wind chosen when he spends the arcane pool point to activate this ability). If he misses with this attack, he can hold the charge for up to 1 minute before it dissipates. At 6th level, and every three levels thereafter, the amount of damage dealt by this attack increases by 1d6.
Pool Strike, Arcing		KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Pool Strike (Arcing)			SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 additional point from his arcane pool when using the pool strike arcana. If his attack hits, the Ruby Arcana can target a number of enemies within 15 feet equal to his Charisma modifier (minimum 0) with a ranged touch attack as a free action. Those struck take the same elemental damage as the primary target of the pool strike, including increased damage on a critical hit. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 12, pool strike ruby arcana
Pool Strike, Clinging		KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Pool Strike (Clinging)			SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 additional point from his arcane pool when making a pool strike. A single target of his pool strike takes elemental damage as normal from the pool strike and also takes half this amount of damage at the beginning of its turn on the following round. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 9, pool strike ruby arcana
Prescient Attack			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Prescient Attack				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool as an immediate action after hitting a target with a weapon attack, allowing him to anticipate his opponent's defenses. The target is denied its Dexterity bonus against the Ruby Arcana's attacks until the end of the Ruby Arcana's next turn. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 6
Prescient Defense			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Prescient Defense				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend 1 point from his arcane pool as an immediate action after hitting a target with a weapon attack, granting him a premonition of his enemy's intentions. The Ruby Arcana gains a bonus to his AC and on Reflex saves equal to his Charisma modifier (minimum 0) against attacks by that opponent until the beginning of his next turn. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 9
Quickened Magic			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Quickened Magic				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Quicken Spell feat. This does not increase the MP cost or the level of the spell. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 15
Reflection				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Reflection					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can sacrifice 1 or more points from his arcane pool as an immediate action to reflect a spell back at its caster. This functions as reflect, but only if the targeted spell is of a level equal to or lower than the number of points expended. If insufficient points are expended, they instead grant an insight bonus on any saving throws allowed by the spell, equal to the number of points spent. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 15
Rod Mastery				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Rod Mastery					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:Whenever the Ruby Arcana uses a rod, he calculates the DC for any spell it contains using his Charisma modifier (minimum 0) instead of the minimum modifier needed to cast a spell of that level.
Rod Wielder				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Rod Wielder					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:The Ruby Arcana adds his Charisma bonus (minimum 0) on caster level checks made to overcome spell resistance when using a spell contained within a rod.
Scroll Mastery			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Scroll Mastery				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:Whenever the Ruby Arcana uses a scroll, he may expend 1 point from his arcane pool to allow him to calculate the DC for any spell contained on the scroll using his Intelligence modifier, instead of the minimum modifier needed cast a spell of that level. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 6
Silent Magic			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Silent Magic				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Silent Spell feat. This does not increase the MP cost or the level of the spell.
Spell Blending			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Spell Blending				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:When a Ruby Arcana selects this arcana, he must select one spell from the black or white mage spell list that is of a Ruby Arcana spell level he can cast. He adds this spell to his list of Ruby Arcana spells known as a Ruby Arcana spell of its black or white mage spell level. He can instead select two spells to add in this way, but both must be at least one level lower than the highest-level Ruby Arcana spell he can cast. A Ruby Arcana can select this Ruby Arcana arcana more than once.
Spell Shield			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Spell Shield				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.176	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can expend a point from his arcane pool as an immediate action to grant himself a shield bonus to AC equal to his Charisma bonus until the end of his next turn.
Spell Trickery			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Spell Trickery				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.177	DESC:When the Ruby Arcana successfully performs a dirty trick combat maneuver, he can cast an illusion or enfeebling spell with a casting time of 1 standard action or less as a swift action. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 12
Spellbreaker			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Spellbreaker				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.177	DESC:The Ruby Arcana gains Spellbreaker as a bonus feat. Prerequisite: Ruby Arcana 9
Still Magic				KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Still Magic					SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.177	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Still Spell feat. This does not increase the MP cost or the level of the spell.
Wand Mastery			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Wand Mastery				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.177	DESC:Whenever the Ruby Arcana uses a wand, he calculates the DC for any spell it contains using his Charisma modifier, instead of the minimum modifier needed to cast a spell of that level.
Wand Wielder			KEY:Ruby Arcana ~ Wand Wielder				SORTKEY:Red Mage Class Feature15b			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ruby Arcana.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.177	DESC:The Ruby Arcana can activate a wand or staff in place of casting a spell when using spell combat.

